e61a5354-0179-4073-bb20-bdd1558a7180	11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111	Annual Community Festival - July 2025	Dear Residents,\n\nWe are thrilled to announce our Annual Community Festival scheduled for July 27-28, 2025! This year's festival promises to be our biggest and most exciting event yet, bringing together families, friends, and neighbors for two days of incredible fun and entertainment.\n\n🎪 EVENT HIGHLIGHTS:\n• Live Music Performances: Featuring local bands and artists from 6 PM to 10 PM both days\n• Food Festival: Over 15 food stalls offering diverse cuisines including Indian, Chinese, Continental, and street food\n• Kids Zone: Face painting, balloon animals, magic shows, and games for children aged 3-12\n• Cultural Performances: Traditional dance shows, singing competitions, and talent showcases\n• Shopping Bazaar: Local artisans and vendors selling handmade crafts, jewelry, and home decor\n• Gaming Arena: Fun activities for all ages including ring toss, darts, and lucky draws\n\n🕐 SCHEDULE:\nDay 1 (July 27): 4 PM - 11 PM\nDay 2 (July 28): 11 AM - 11 PM\n\n📍 VENUE: Community Clubhouse and Garden Area\n\n🎟️ ENTRY: Free for all residents and their guests\nNote: Each household can bring up to 4 guests. Please register guests at the security desk.\n\n🎁 PRIZES & GIVEAWAYS:\n• Grand Prize: 75-inch Smart TV\n• Second Prize: Home Theater System\n• Third Prize: Air Purifier\n• Plus many more exciting prizes throughout the event!\n\n🤝 VOLUNTEER OPPORTUNITIES:\nWe're looking for enthusiastic volunteers to help make this event successful. If you're interested in joining our organizing committee, please contact the management office or reply to this notice.\n\n🎵 SPECIAL PERFORMANCES:\nWe're excited to host the renowned "Melodic Harmony" band on July 28th at 8 PM. They'll be performing popular Bollywood hits and classic rock songs.\n\n🍕 FOOD & BEVERAGES:\nAll food stalls will be operating with special festival pricing. We'll also have complimentary welcome drinks and snacks for the first 100 families each day.\n\n⚠️ IMPORTANT REMINDERS:\n• Parking will be managed by our security team\n• Please bring your own seating arrangements for outdoor performances\n• Event is eco-friendly - please use dustbins provided\n• Photography and videography are welcome and encouraged\n• In case of rain, indoor venues will be arranged\n\nWe look forward to celebrating together as one big community family! Mark your calendars and get ready for an unforgettable weekend.\n\nFor any questions or suggestions, please contact the management office at extension 101 or email us at events@casanirvana.com\n\nBest regards,\nCasa Nirvana Management Team	2025-07-18 09:24:40.561237+00	https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1564013799919-ab600027ffc6?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center	\N	{}	Events Committee	https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=150&h=150&fit=crop&crop=face	event	high	0	0	t	2025-09-22 14:49:11.907294+00	2025-07-18 09:24:40.561237+00	published
