4de29247-a92a-4762-82f6-ac829b9b0484	11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111	New Property Management System Launch	Dear Casa Nirvana Residents,\n\nWe are excited to announce the launch of our new comprehensive property management system! This modern platform will revolutionize how we manage our beautiful community.\n\nKey Features:\n• Digital notice board with real-time updates\n• Online maintenance request system\n• Community event calendar\n• Resident directory and communication tools\n• Amenity booking system\n• Bill payment integration\n\nBenefits for Residents:\n✓ Instant access to community announcements\n✓ Track maintenance requests in real-time\n✓ Easy communication with management\n✓ Convenient amenity reservations\n✓ Streamlined bill payments\n\nThe system is now live and accessible through our mobile app. All residents will receive login credentials via email within the next 24 hours.\n\nTraining sessions will be conducted next week:\n📅 Monday, July 21st - 10:00 AM (English)\n📅 Tuesday, July 22nd - 2:00 PM (Hindi)\n📅 Wednesday, July 23rd - 6:00 PM (English)\n\nLocation: Community Hall\n\nFor technical support, please contact our IT team at support@casanirvana.com or call the management office.\n\nThank you for your cooperation in making Casa Nirvana a smarter, more connected community!\n\nBest regards,\nCasa Nirvana Management Team	2025-07-18 09:38:22.952396+00	https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?w=800&h=600&fit=crop&crop=center	\N	{}	Property Manager	\N	announcement	high	0	0	t	2025-09-22 14:49:11.907294+00	2025-07-18 09:38:22.952396+00	published
